translation.en: [paramedic 1] We have a female patient, unconscious with a head injury.
translation.zh:
‎调度 742 女性病人一名
‎头部受伤 无意识

translation.en: [paramedic 2] Olivia, can you hear me?
translation.zh: ‎奥利维亚 听到了吗？ ‎（澳大利亚 悉尼）

translation.en: -Olivia, can you hear me? -[gasps]
-[cardiac monitor beeping] -[Olivia] Fuck.
-Look, it's okay. It's okay. No. -[paramedic 2] You're okay.
translation.zh:
‎-该死
‎-没事的 ‎-没事的 别
‎-你没事 你在救护车里

translation.en: -You're in an ambulance. -No, no. I need to--
translation.zh:
‎-没事的 别
‎-你没事 你在救护车里 ‎不 我得…

translation.en: -[monitor beeping rapidly] -Let me out.
-It's okay. -Off. Off.
-[paramedic 1] Stop. -What is-- Let me out!
-Miss Healy-- -Oh, my boob!
What? No, I need to get home!
translation.zh:
‎-什么？不 我得回家！
‎-抓住她！

translation.en: -[paramedic 2] Grab her! -Oh, God! I wanna go home!
[man] Sorry. My bad.
-[Olivia] That's too much eye contact. -[man] Okay.
-[panting] Oh, shit, I'm coming. -[man] Okay.
-You need to skedaddle. -Oh.
-You don't wanna grab a bite? -Well, I can't.
translation.zh:
‎-不想一起吃点什么吗？
‎-不行啊

translation.en: I wanna say, Kevin?
-Tomorrow? -No can do.
I'll be in Australia tomorrow.
Right.
No, really. It's my best friend's 40th.
translation.zh: ‎不 真的 我最好的朋友过40岁生日

translation.en: I'm flying in for the weekend to surprise her.
Your life is intense.
Yeah, well, existence is random, life is short.
translation.zh: ‎是啊 生得随机 生命短暂

translation.en: If you're not making the most of every moment, what's the fucking point?
translation.zh:
‎如果你不充分利用每一刻
‎还有什么意义？

translation.en: Okay. Ow.
♪ I've been so good all of my life ♪
-Hey. -Yo, Liv.
My wife loved that bar you recommended.
translation.zh: ‎我老婆很喜欢你推荐的酒吧

translation.en: [Liv] Told you the oysters would work.
Here she is.
Here we go.
Hi, Valerie.
I'm not gonna hassle you about being a judge for the new TV show.
translation.zh: ‎我不会为做新电视节目评委的事烦你

translation.en: Although, I do stand by my original pitch.
"World's top chefs being judged by Banquet's top food writer."
translation.zh:
‎“世界顶尖厨师
‎由《宴会》顶级美食作家来评委”

translation.en: Me. I'd watch the shit out of it.
I know I'm not the obvious choice, but I think--
translation.zh: ‎我知道我不是首选 但我…

translation.en: I'd watch the shit out of it too.
In fact, I think a million people across 120 territories
translation.zh: ‎事实上 我认为120个地区的一百万人

translation.en: would watch the shit out of it.
You're my pick.
Get the fuck out.
-Your writing's on point. -Oh, my God.
You got a palate like no one else.
All the best chefs respect you,
and this whole Australian thing, I can sell it.
translation.zh: ‎还有澳大利亚的出身 可以营销一下

translation.en: Oh, my God. I can't feel my face.
Is this really happening? Is my face being weird?
One problem.
Outside the food industry, Liv Healy means nothing.
translation.zh: ‎在美食界之外 利维希利毫无名气

translation.en: Oh, wow, harsh.
-It's true, but harsh. -The show execs see you as a wild card.
translation.zh:
‎-是真的 但很残忍
‎-节目高管认为你是不定因素

translation.en: I need to prove to them
that your voice can reach an audience outside the food industry.
translation.zh: ‎你的声音能触及美食界之外的人

translation.en: Sure.
How, exactly?
I need you to write an article.
Yeah, I need you to write something that raises your profile globally.
translation.zh:
‎我需要你写点
‎能在全球范围内提升你形象的东西

translation.en: The execs need to see you reach a large audience,
translation.zh: ‎得让高管看到你触及更大的受众

translation.en: build familiarity, go viral.
The show launches in four weeks. Let's talk tomorrow. We'll talk strategy.
translation.zh:
‎节目四周后开播
‎我们明天再谈 聊聊策略

translation.en: Can we make it Monday? Gotta go to Australia for the weekend.
translation.zh:
‎可以周一再谈吗？
‎我周末得回澳大利亚

translation.en: Yeah. Yes. Have your fun.
Yeah.
Come Monday, it's on.
Seriously, this is gonna take you from Stefani Germanotta
translation.zh: ‎真的 这会让你从史蒂芬妮吉马诺塔

translation.en: to Lady fucking Gaga.
Oh, I fucking love her.
Okay, I gotta bounce. My dog needs her epilepsy meds.
translation.zh: ‎好 我得走了 我的狗需要服癫痫药

translation.en: -I'll talk to you soon. -Yeah.
-This is huge. -Wow.
-Don't fuck it up. -Uh-huh.
I'm celebrating.
Yum.
Damn. Yes.
-Cheers. -Thank you.
[stewardess] Ladies and gentlemen, we'll shortly begin our descent into Sydney,
translation.zh: ‎女士们 先生们 我们即将在悉尼降落

translation.en: where it's hot at 38 degrees.
-Fuck me dead. How's the fucking humidity? -Welcome to Sydney, mate.
translation.zh:
‎-可恶 怎么这么潮湿？
‎-欢迎来到悉尼

translation.en: ♪ Happy birthday to you ♪
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪
♪ Happy birthday, dear Amy-- ♪
translation.zh: ‎祝你生日快乐 亲爱的艾米

translation.en: Amy!
Holy fuck!
I know! Here's the best present ever!
translation.zh: ‎我知道 这是史上最棒的礼物

translation.en: Don't see how this tops the air fryer we got her.
translation.zh: ‎天啊！ ‎这怎么能跟我们给她买的空气炸锅比

translation.en: What?
-Hi. -This is the best present ever.
Oh, I'm so happy you're here.
Oh, as if I'd miss it, you maniac.
translation.zh: ‎我怎么会错过 你个疯子

translation.en: -Here. -Oh. What-- Here, hold all this.
I'm gonna make a toast.
Oh, I'm just gonna grab that. Thank you.
-Okay. -[woman] I was drinking that.
Hello, everyone! Hello! Hi!
Amy Kwan,
you are a beautiful, flawless person.
You've been my ride-or-die since high school and my soul mate.
translation.zh:
‎你从高中起
‎就是我的搭档和灵魂伴侣

translation.en: -[Amy] Aw. -And there is no one in the world that I--
Oh, shit.
Holy fuck.
Let's get the party started!
♪ You can call me the good-time girl ♪
-Oh, wake up, boofhead. -[Liv groans]
Get out!
Oh, you stink.
God!
Far out. What are you doing here anyway?
Oh, wedding stuff with Mum.
-Welcome home. -Oh, get out.
Oh, Mum, so the celebrant is confirmed, but I spoke to the florist.
translation.zh:
‎妈妈 主持人已经确认
‎但我联络过花商

translation.en: Unfortunately, the peonies will be out of season.
We'll just have to go with the lilies.
Oh, that's a shame. You love peonies.
translation.zh: ‎太可惜了 你那么喜欢牡丹

translation.en: But the lilies will be just as pretty. Don't you think, Liv?
translation.zh: ‎但百合花也一样漂亮 不是吗 利维？

translation.en: Wonder what your gay ancestors would think
about you entering into an antiquated institution
that's predominantly about oppression and ownership.
translation.zh: ‎一个以压迫和所有为主的制度

translation.en: That I'm making it fabulous.
Some vitamin C.
Strawsie?
-Yes! -Wow.
This level of pathetic is hard to watch.
Says the guy who visits his mum five times a week, Gaz.
translation.zh:
‎每周来看妈妈五次的人
‎还好意思说 盖斯

translation.en: -It's not that often. -I love having you both home.
translation.zh:
‎-没那么频繁
‎-我喜欢你们俩都在家

translation.en: -Now, what do you want for dinner? -[Liv] Surprise me.
-Oh! No. Your lamb chops. Delectable. -[Gaz] Hmm.
I have some big news.
Picture this.
Internationally renowned chefs compete to be crowned world's best.
translation.zh: ‎国际知名厨师争夺世界第一的名号

translation.en: Coming this fall, Banquet Royale, your newest food obsession.
translation.zh:
‎今秋来袭 《皇家宴会》
‎你的新美食痴迷

translation.en: It's a TV show, and I'm one of the judges.
translation.zh: ‎是一部电视节目 我是评委之一

translation.en: But, wait, aren't you a writer?
A great writer. And that's why they want me, my voice,
translation.zh: ‎好作家 所以他们想找我 要我发声

translation.en: so I can share my taste with, like, a gajillion people.
translation.zh: ‎让我跟数亿人分享我的品位

translation.en: Do you know who is a wonderful cook?
Andrea Seidelman.
Do you remember her from netball?
-Oh, her dad was hot. -Oh, her dad was hot.
translation.zh:
‎-她爸爸很性感
‎-她爸爸很性感

translation.en: Well, she cooked the most delicious date slice
for the surf club fundraiser.
What's this got to do with anything?
Well, I was just saying it was very moist.
Oh, I'm so sorry. I didn't realize it was moist.
translation.zh: ‎对不起 我不知道是润的

translation.en: [Lorraine] Oh, Olivia.
-I need some air. -[Gaz] Hmm.
Oh, that's--
Mum, that's a health hazard.
[Liv] Your face is a health hazard.
Forget it. I'll find a whistleblower willing to go on record.
translation.zh: ‎算了 我找个愿意公开的举报人吧

translation.en: Uh, Evie, can you pause TikTok and go make your bed?
translation.zh:
‎伊薇 你能先把TikTok暂停
‎去收拾床吗？

translation.en: You can't pause TikTok.
If you wanna go to Sarah's, get upstairs now.
translation.zh: ‎如果你想去莎拉家 马上上楼

translation.en: God, you need to chill, Amy.
translation.zh: ‎天啊 别那么激动 艾米

translation.en: That's "Mum" to you.
[in Cantonese] Her attitude stinks lately.
Just like you at that age.
-Just got the bill from yesterday. -Mmm.
Didn't look like a $700 table.
At least it was a memorable birthday.
Yeah, it's pretty cool Liv flew halfway around the world for you.
translation.zh: ‎利维为你飞过半个地球真是不错

translation.en: But you organized a beautiful lunch.
translation.zh: ‎但是你安排了一个场美妙的午宴

translation.en: In fact, you're so sweet and understanding,
translation.zh: ‎而且 你这么贴心 善解人意

translation.en: you probably wouldn't mind if I took my best friend to the awards tonight.
translation.zh:
‎应该不会介意我今晚带好闺蜜
‎去参加颁奖

translation.en: Oh! First I'm down 700 bucks, now this.
translation.zh:
‎应该不会介意我今晚带好闺蜜
‎去参加颁奖 ‎我先是赔了700澳元 现在又这样

translation.en: Oh, Liv's heard me bang on about the AJAs since uni.
translation.zh:
‎利维从大学时
‎就老听我说澳新闻奖的事

translation.en: Please?
Fine. I'll watch a movie in my tux.
translation.zh: ‎好吧 那我就穿着燕尾服看电影

translation.en: You're the best.
Oh, you little shit. That's my stuff!
Come here! Call the authorities!
Oh, no, they're expensive.
Oh, God!
Wait! Oh. Oh, it hurts!
-Oh, my God. -Are you okay?
-Oh, it's just the kid's got my shit. -Come with me.
translation.zh:
‎-那小子拿了我的东西
‎-跟我来

translation.en: [Liv] You're the cops. Really, that's all you can do?
translation.zh: ‎你们是警察 就只能做到这个吗？

translation.en: My green card is in that bag, and I cannot be stranded here,
translation.zh:
‎我的绿卡在那个袋子里
‎我可不能困在这里

translation.en: so can you please let me know if it shows up?
Yeah, I know it's slim odds, but…
Thanks. NWA were right.
translation.zh: ‎谢谢 尼哥有态度嘻哈团说得对

translation.en: Some alkalized water?
Oh, yes, thank you.
Your aura is very purple.
Wow, it just went bright red.
Here, let me cleanse it for you.
Okay. Thank you, nice lady, for the magic water, but I'm gonna head off.
translation.zh: ‎谢谢 好心小姐  ‎谢谢你的魔法水 但我要走了

translation.en: Wait. Wait.
I have something for you.
Hematite.
It will ground and stabilize you.
translation.zh: ‎它会让你脚踏实地 稳定下来

translation.en: I don't need to be grounded.
I have a flight tomorrow and no green card.
translation.zh: ‎我明天还要赶飞机 却没有绿卡

translation.en: I need to figure out how to get back into the US.
Yeah, I don't think we have that crystal.
Yeah, no shit. I don't need a crystal, I need a--
translation.zh: ‎当然 我不需要水晶 我需要…

translation.en: I need a miracle worker.
You're a miracle worker.
Thank you. I owe you big time.
Right, my contact got you an appointment at the US consulate tomorrow at 10.
translation.zh:
‎我的朋友给你安排了明天10点
‎去美国领事馆跟人会面

translation.en: They'll give you a travel document, and you'll be good to make your flight.
translation.zh:
‎他们会给你签发旅行证件
‎你下午就可以赶航班了

translation.en: You are one well-connected goddess. Thank you.
translation.zh: ‎你真是个有人脉的女神 谢谢

translation.en: I am. And can't smoke in here, okay?
translation.zh: ‎是啊 这里不可以抽烟 好吗？

translation.en: Trying to teach my preteen drugs are bad. I can't let her know I'm a hypocrite.
translation.zh:
‎我在教育我家准青春期儿童
‎毒品不好 ‎我不能让他们知道我是伪君子

translation.en: Ooh, that's good.
Right, what am I gonna wear?
-What do we think of this? -Ah, serious BVE.
translation.zh:
‎-你觉得这个怎么样？
‎-骚气冲天

translation.en: -Big vag energy. -Get fucked. I've had two kids.
translation.zh:
‎-很有骚气的意思
‎-滚蛋 我都有两个孩子了

translation.en: Oh, God, it's a compliment. -Oh. -It's like-- Yeah.
translation.zh: ‎我的天啊 这是夸奖 是好事

translation.en: Have you written your acceptance speech yet?
-I'm just happy to be nominated. -That is absolute bullshit, Kwan.
translation.zh:
‎-能提名我就很高兴了
‎-胡说八道 关

translation.en: -I know you wanna win. -Yeah, of course, but you can't say that.
translation.zh:
‎-我知道你想赢
‎-当然了 但不能这么说

translation.en: Why not? You're the shit.
Okay, it doesn't mean this Asian woman will win up against four men called Chris.
translation.zh:
‎那也不代表一个亚裔女人
‎能赢过四个叫克里斯的男人

translation.en: Cool. All right, well, what about your gracious loser face?
translation.zh: ‎好 那你的未得奖体面表情呢

translation.en: Oh, yeah.
Oh, no. Stop it. You look constipated at best. No.
translation.zh: ‎不 停下 你像是在便秘 不

translation.en: Oh, I'm bad at this.
-Yes. -Okay.
So I was thinking, why don't you just come with me tonight?
translation.zh: ‎我在想 你今晚跟我一起来吧？

translation.en: What?
And walk into a room full of people who have either rejected me or fired me?
translation.zh:
‎去一个坐满了
‎拒绝过我或解雇过我的人的房间？

translation.en: -Yeah. -That's my idea of hell.
Yeah, I know.
It's the reason I moved to New York, and you know that.
translation.zh: ‎这就是我搬去纽约的原因 你知道的

translation.en: Oh, but come on, now you're killing it. Okay?
translation.zh: ‎拜托 你现在多厉害 好吧？

translation.en: What is the best revenge?
If you say living well, I will punch you in your perky bosoms.
translation.zh:
‎如果你说活得逍遥
‎我就锤你坚挺的胸

translation.en: No, shoving your success in the face of those arseholes.
translation.zh: ‎不 是在那些混蛋面前炫耀你的成功

translation.en: You're gonna be a judge on a fancy TV show,
translation.zh: ‎你要去高级电视节目做评委了

translation.en: and I did just call in a massive favor to get you that consulate appointment.
translation.zh:
‎况且我才卖了个大人情
‎才帮你安排了领事馆的会面

translation.en: Fine, I'll come.
But only if I can wear this.
Oh, I dare you.
Remember when I had sex with Doug's brother at your wedding?
translation.zh:
‎记得我在你婚礼上
‎和道格的弟弟上了床吗？

translation.en: -What? -What?
[woman] Thank you. Yes. Thanks very much. Appreciate it.
-Hi. -[Lorraine] Oh, hi, darling.
-Hi, Mary. -Heard about your ordeal with your bag.
translation.zh:
‎-嗨 玛丽
‎-听说你包包的倒霉事了

translation.en: -Yeah. -Want a lollipop?
-Yes. Yes, I do. Oh, thank you. -This is a nice surprise.
-What are you doing here? -I just need to see Dr. Price.
translation.zh:
‎-你来这里做什么？
‎-我只想见普莱斯医生

translation.en: Why, what's wrong?
That is between me and the physician.
Also, I have to bail on dinner tonight. Sorry.
translation.zh: ‎而且 今晚的晚饭我不能吃了 抱歉

translation.en: I promised Amy I'd be her date at the Journalism Awards.
translation.zh: ‎我答应做艾米的新闻奖晚宴女伴了

translation.en: So you choose her over your family.
translation.zh: ‎所以你选择她而不是你的家人

translation.en: Amy is family, Mum.
But more importantly, can I please get a lift to the consulate tomorrow?
translation.zh:
‎但更重要的是
‎明天可以送我去趟领事馆吗？

translation.en: -I need to get a new green card. -Why are you rushing back to New York?
translation.zh:
‎-我得换张绿卡
‎-你为什么急着回纽约？

translation.en: You're here now. Why not stay till the wedding?
translation.zh:
‎你都回来了
‎为什么不留下来参加婚礼？

translation.en: Mum, the TV show. Huge, life-altering opportunity.
translation.zh: ‎妈妈 电视节目 改变人生的天大机会

translation.en: Well, I'm taking Gareth and Dalbert for a suit fitting in the morning.
translation.zh: ‎我上午要送盖瑞斯和达伯特去试西装

translation.en: Oh, perfect. I'll just hitch a ride with you and Galbert.
translation.zh: ‎好 我搭你和盖伯特的便车就行

translation.en: Or DalGaz.
How about Gazert?
Yes, Mary. Up top.
I don't normally prescribe benzodiazepines.
It's just to take the edge off this shitastic event I've got tonight.
translation.zh:
‎只是为了让我在今晚的疯狂活动上
‎不那么紧张

translation.en: -My New York doctor gives them like candy. -Well, this isn't New York.
translation.zh:
‎我在纽约的医生拿它们当糖开 ‎-这里不是纽约
‎-我知道

translation.en: I know.
How have you been generally?
Yeah. I've got the constitution of an ox.
-I still party like I'm 20. -I know.
I follow you on Instagram.
Oh, good on you for keeping up with technology.
translation.zh: ‎你真棒 还能跟上新技术

translation.en: Ooh, this can't be right.
That's far too high for someone your age.
translation.zh: ‎对于你这个年纪的人来说太高了

translation.en: Oh, it's probably spiked because all of my shit was stolen today,
translation.zh:
‎可能是因为我的物品今天被偷了
‎才会飚高

translation.en: and Mum is on my back because I can't make dinner tonight.
translation.zh:
‎今晚我又不能回家吃饭
‎还被妈妈念叨

translation.en: -Oh, Lorraine. She's a firecracker. -Yes.
translation.zh:
‎-洛琳 她真是个暴脾气
‎-是的

translation.en: But it must be nice to catch up with your mum and dad though.
translation.zh: ‎不过 能跟爸妈叙叙旧很好吧

translation.en: Dad's been dead for 24 years,
and as his doctor, that's either one hell of a misdiagnosis,
translation.zh: ‎作为他的医生 这要么是严重误诊

translation.en: or you know something that I don't.
Oh, goodness me.
I do apologize. I don't know what I was thinking.
translation.zh: ‎对不起 我不知道是怎么想的

translation.en: Yeah.
It's a lot in there, I know.
-The who's who of Aussie journalism. -More like the who's that.
translation.zh:
‎-澳大利亚的新闻界名人
‎-无名还差不多

translation.en: Amy. Sending all the good vibrations your way.
Liv Healy, this is Jeremy Jackson, lifestyle writer for Standard.
translation.zh:
‎利维希利 这是杰里米杰克逊
‎《标准》的生活方式作家

translation.en: -Namaste. -Namaste.
Okay, let's get a lot of drinks into us.
Ah, ah, ah. No, I need both of these. This place is a battlefield.
translation.zh: ‎不 我需要这两样 这里就是战场

translation.en: I really wanna show Helen
that out-of-office Amy is cool while still being professional.
translation.zh:
‎离开办公室的艾米
‎又酷又能保持专业水准

translation.en: -Are you a bit obsessed with your boss? -Yeah, she's terrifying.
translation.zh:
‎-你是迷上你的上司了吗？
‎-是啊 她好可怕

translation.en: I love her. Hey, wanna mingle?
translation.zh: ‎我爱她 想不想去交际一下？

translation.en: Fuck no. I hate everyone here except you.
translation.zh: ‎不要 我讨厌这里除你之外的所有人

translation.en: But you go and do your thing. I love you.
Steven Rogers.
Olivia Healy.
Nice to meet you.
I actually interned for you when you were at the Star.
translation.zh:
‎你在《星空》的时候
‎我给你做过实习生

translation.en: You used to text me after hours and complain about your wife.
translation.zh:
‎你以前下班后会给我发短信
‎抱怨你老婆

translation.en: -You must be thinking of someone else. -No, definitely you.
translation.zh:
‎-你说的一定是别人
‎-不 绝对是你

translation.en: You also shut down all my pitches, said I was a "shallow thinker."
translation.zh:
‎你还毙掉了我所有的照片
‎说我“思想浅薄”

Only this year, one of our stories

Move.

Fuck.

Far out.
God!

‎既然我这么让人受不了

[whispers] Far out.

‎-好吧 一切东西都就绪

Ma'am? Ma'am?

After your incident, the consulate deemed that your poor health

As one of two consulate-approved doctors in Sydney,

translation.en: No!
Oh, shit, I'm sorry.

‎-你不了解我
